---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sendbook — Etalase Digital Satu Halaman untuk UMKM</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #0a0a0a;
            --text: #f5f5f7;
            --text-dim: #a1a1aa;
            --accent: #6366f1;
            --accent-hover: #818cf8;
            --surface: #18181b;
            --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        }
        * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .logo { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.25rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
        .logo span { color: var(--accent); }
        nav a {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        nav a:hover { color: var(--text); }
        main {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .hero { text-align: center; max-width: 640px; }
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(99,102,241,0.1);
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.2);
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            line-height: 1.15;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
        p {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .cta {
            display: inline-flex;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--accent-hover); transform: scale(1.02); }
        .btn-secondary {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--surface);
            color: var(--text);
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 3.5rem;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .feature { padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: 12px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
        .feature h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
        .feature p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 0; }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            h1 { font-size: 2.25rem; }
            .features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="logo">send<span>book</span></div>
        <a href="https://github.com/myo rca-sys/sendbook">GitHub</a>
    </nav>
    <main>
        <div class="hero">
            <div class="badge">Beta — Indonesia</div>
            <h1>Etalase digital <span>satu halaman</span> untuk UMKM</h1>
            <p>Buat toko online dalam 5 menit. Cukup satu link, pelanggan bisa lihat produk dan langsung chat WhatsApp.</p>
            <div class="cta">
                <a href="#" class="btn-primary">Buat Toko Gratis</a>
                <a href="#" class="btn-secondary">Lihat Contoh</a>
            </div>
            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>⚡ Satu Halaman</h3>
                    <p>Pelanggan lihat semua produk dalam satu tampilan cepat. No app loading.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>💬 WhatsApp</h3>
                    <p>Klik produk → langsung chat WhatsApp. Pesanan tercatat otomatis.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>📊 Analytics</h3>
                    <p>Lihat berapa orang lihat toko & klik produk. Ukur minat pasar.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>&copy; {year} Sendbook — Dibuat untuk UMKM Indonesia</footer>
</body>
</html>
